    "DALL•E, stable diffusion or Midjourney.Procedure The whole study lasts 30-40 minutes in total.",
    "After welcoming the participant, the researcher describes the study and obtains informed consent.",
    "Next, the researcher describes the study design, which consists of two 12-minute tasks: a moodboard baseline task and a GenAI task.",
    "Participants are asked to use a talk-aloud protocol to describe their strategies for finding images or creating prompts.",
    "The researcher offers a short tutorial for participants who lack experience either with moodboarding or using GenAI.Moodboard task (baseline condition): Participants are asked to create a moodboard that expresses a visual concept for a café interior in the style of their choice."
